import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { AuthService } from '../auth.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-product-master-registration', templateUrl: './product-master-registration.component.html', styleUrls: ['./product-master-registration.component.css'] }) export class ProductMasterRegistrationComponent { constructor(private registerService:AuthService, private router:Router) { } handleRegister(form:any){ console.log(form.value); this.registerService.registerProductMaster(form.value).subscribe({ next:(responce)=>{ console.log(responce); } }) } }
